UAObjectType.Description: This event type is used for PROFINET diagnosis events.

This event is fired when a new asset (device, real module, real submodule or asset) is detected, an asset was removed, or the data of an asset changed. An asset change for a device, real module or real submodule means that its I&M data has changed.
